# Version bump on every change

When modifying any project file (except docs-only), increment the app version:

1. In `sw.js`: bump `CACHE_NAME` — e.g. `libero-v13` → `libero-v14`
2. In `index.html`: set the same number in all `?v=` query params (`style.css`, `scripts.js`, `sw.js`)

Keep both in sync so Service Worker and static assets invalidate together.
